      <p><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Access_control_CORS">CORS访问控制</a>&nbsp;<a href="#fnref:1" class="reversefootnote">&#8617;</a></p>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>

